Tyelknowle

Overview

tie-ELK-nole

Gender: Male

Race: ElfWood Elf

Class: Cleric

Age: Youth41 / Looks 14

Identifying Marks: thin, very muscular, scars along back, arms, and legs (from brutal whippings).

Character Sheet: PC Tyelknowle (Chris).pdf

Height: 5'3, Weight: 97lbs, Eyes: Copper, Skin: Greenish Tan, Hair: Black (Short rough cut)

Motivation and Philosophy

Long Term Aspirations: He will have to deal with the slavers that attacked his tribe, he just isn't sure how yet.

Short Term Aspirations: Complete his pilgrimage for Tymora and become a more active member in the church (which is to say be an adventurer).

Personal Life

Friends: Burt - Pet Mouse [Bael'Ru]

Family: Mother: Kayleilii

Father: Tassarinluss

Brother: Kaytietus (Dead)

Contacts: Jurras Bigglesworth - member of the Church of Tymora in Waterdeep

Father Franz - He was the man at the church on DT06 that Ty brought Joclynn to.

Possessions

A receipt of Deposit for a bank in a far flung city.

Receipt # 71149
City - Phsant in the country of Thesk (far to the East).

As a member of the Mud-Blood Family, I robbed a noble from the Utter East (Asian Culture). I made out with some copper, silver, and this slip of paper. He vowed to slay me, mostly for keeping the paper. I don't know what it is to, but I kept it and laughed at him. The coin is spent, but the paper reminds me to be brave and helps me dream of far-off places.

Carries a dagger with the text “Reszur” inscribed on the handle.

Identity

Internal: Raised as a slave for over 15 years, he was brutalized in horrible ways. He still has nightmares about it and can't think/believe his parents are still alive because of how hard that would be and what it might drive him to do.

External: Always planning, always whispering.

 

Tyelknowle speaks to his pet mouse, Burt (Bael'Ru), even when Burt is not seen. He forms plans and bounces ideas off the tiny rodent and usually does so in elf but will switch to common at times.

 

Those who don't know him, may think he is just talking to himself.

Background

Backstory: Tyelknowle Backstory

Collaborative Adventure: Tyelknowle Collaborative Adventure

Shared Collaborative Adventures: Rowena Collaborative Adventure & Grimble Collaborative Adventure
